data.description: Welcome home! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence exudes warmth and character at every turn. Step inside to discover a beautifully designed floor plan. This move-in ready home offers single-level living, with a convenient 1-car garage, and great outdoor space for enjoyment and entertainment. Its prime location ensures easy access to amenities and attractions, making it a suitable choice for both starters and downsizers alike. Don't miss the opportunity to call this delightful house your home sweet home! Measurements approximate.
